snippet.description:

Song: The Thaandavam 
Music : Thaman S
Lyrics: Kalyan Chakravarthy
Singers : Shankar Mahadevan, Kailash Kher, Deepak Blue

Song Programmed & Arranged by: Thaman S
Beat & EDM Works: Beyond Sound (T)
Live percussions - Thaman S, Anandan Sivamani, The Gongura Band 
Drums of India - Anandan Sivamani 
Chenda - The Gongura Band
Ethnic Indian Strings - Subhani
Additional Programming: Shashank Alamuru, Osho V, Hari S R

snippet.title: Mowgli Teaser | Roshan Kanakala | Sandeep Raj | Bandi Saroj Kumar | Sakkshi | TG Vishwa Prasad | PMF
snippet.description:
Mowgli is an upcoming unique romantic action drama set deep within a forest backdrop. Directed by National Award-winning filmmaker Sandeep Raj (Colour Photo), Produced by TG Vishwa Prasad and Krithi Prasad under People Media Factory Banner.The film has cinematography by Rama Maruthi M, while Kaala Bhairava scores the music. The work is co-written by Rama Maruthi M and Radhakrishna Reddy The technical team also includes Peekay as editor, Kiran Mamidi as art director, and Natraj Madigonda choreographing the action sequences.

Mowgli 2025 will arrive in cinemas on December 12th, 2025.

Cast: Roshan Kanakala, Sakkshi Mhadolkar, Bandi Saroj Kumar & Harsha Chemudu

Technical Crew:
Writer & Director: Sandeep Raj
Producers: TG Vishwa Prasad, Krithi Prasad
Banner: People Media Factory
Music: Kaala Bhairava
DOP: Rama Maruti M
Editor: Peekay 
Art: Kiran Mamidi
Chief Executive Producer : Sujith Kumar kolli
Action: Natraj Madigonda
Co-writers: Rama Maruthi. M & Radhakrishna Reddy
Costume Designers : G V Annapurna and Sushmitha¬†Bommidi
Publicity Designer : Suryah.psd (Suresh Muddavaram)
Teaser cut : Kalyan Surya Prakash

snippet.title: Easily 3 Star the Last Town Hall 17 Challenge (Clash of Clans)
snippet.description:
How to 3 Star the Last TH17 Challenge in Clash of Clans. Judo Sloth provides a tutorial for the new event attack which showcases the 3 Star by Cronos of Tribe Gaming in the World Championship final. Being a full attack, and a 9 Healer Hero Charge, it will be tricky if you're not a TH17 player, but I've broken it down into steps so that with a bit of practice you'll be able to beat the challenge. Best of luck with your 3 stars though and thank you for supporting the channel with Code Judo!

snippet.title: The Devil Wears Prada 2 | Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
A sequel? For spring? Groundbreaking. Meryl Streep, Anne Hathaway, Emily Blunt, and Stanley Tucci return in The Devil Wears Prada 2, in theaters May 1, 2026. Watch the teaser trailer now.¬†

Almost twenty years after making their iconic turns as Miranda, Andy, Emily and Nigel‚ÄîMeryl Streep, Anne Hathaway, Emily Blunt and Stanley Tucci return to the fashionable streets of New York City and the sleek offices of Runway Magazine in the eagerly awaited sequel to the 2006 phenomenon that defined a generation. 
 
The film reunites the original main cast with director David Frankel and writer Aline Brosh McKenna, and introduces an all-new runway of characters including Kenneth Branagh, Simone Ashley, Justin Theroux, Lucy Liu, Patrick Brammall, Caleb Hearon, Helen J. Shen, Pauline Chalamet, B.J. Novak and Conrad Ricamora. Tracie Thoms and Tibor Feldman also reprise their roles as ‚ÄúLily‚Äù and ‚ÄúIrv‚Äù from the first film. 
 
‚ÄúThe Devil Wears Prada 2‚Äù is produced by Wendy Finerman, and executive produced by Michael Bederman, Karen Rosenfelt and McKenna. The film debuts exclusively in theaters May 1, 2026.

snippet.title: "Wuthering Heights" | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Inspired by the greatest love story of all time. ‚ÄúWuthering Heights‚Äù only in theaters this Valentine‚Äôs Day. #WutheringHeightsMovie

Pre-order Charli xcx's new album "Wuthering Heights": https://wutheringheights.charlixcx.com/

From Warner Bros. Pictures and Academy Award and BAFTA-winning filmmaker Emerald Fennell comes ‚ÄúWUTHERING HEIGHTS,‚Äù starring Academy Award and BAFTA nominee Margot Robbie opposite BAFTA nominee Jacob Elordi.

A bold and original imagining of one of the greatest love stories of all time, Emerald Fennell‚Äôs ‚ÄúWUTHERING HEIGHTS‚Äù stars Margot Robbie as Cathy and Jacob Elordi as Heathcliff, whose forbidden passion for one another turns from romantic to intoxicating in an epic tale of lust, love and madness.

The film also stars alongside Oscar nominee Hong Chau, Shazad Latif, Alison Oliver, BAFTA winner Martin Clunes and Ewan Mitchell.

Fennell directs from her own screenplay, and produces alongside Oscar nominee and BAFTA award winner Josey McNamara and Robbie. Oscar nominee Tom Ackerley and Sara Desmond are executive producing.

Behind the scenes, Fennell worked with such frequent collaborators as Oscar- and BAFTA-winning director of photography Linus Sandgren, Oscar- and BAFTA-nominated production designer Suzie Davies, BAFTA-nominated editor Victoria Boydell, award-winning casting director Kharmel Cochrane and BAFTA-nominated composer Anthony Willis. Oscar and BAFTA winner Jacqueline Durran designed the costumes. Original songs by Charli XCX.

Warner Bros. Pictures and MRC Present A Lie Still & LuckyChap Entertainment Production, a film by Emerald Fennell, ‚ÄúWUTHERING HEIGHTS.‚Äù Distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures, the film will be in theaters nationwide on February 13, 2026, and internationally beginning 11 February.

snippet.description:

‚ù§Ô∏è‚Äçüî• Song out now

#EkDeewaneKiDEEWANIYAT Booking open: https://bookmy.show/HI_EDKD

In Cinemas Now!

Music : Rahul Mishra 
Lyrics : Prince Dubey 
Singer : B Praak
Music producer : The Rish

PlayDMF Team :-
Founder & CEO : Anshul Garg

Head : Amit Sharma 
Team : Nagesh Jadhav, Kajal Israni, Amol Suryavanshi, Lavanya Das & Nishtha Sikroria

https://www.virginmusic.com/

Lyrics :-
Chaahe ye zamana badal bhi jaaye
Aa jaaye yahan daur koi
Dil mein hamesha tum hi rahoge
Na aayega aur koi 

Hum bas tere hain 
Jab tak jiyenge tere hi rahenge
Hum ye kah rahe hain
Hum toh tere hain tere hi rahenge 

Rasta ek ho tera mera yahan 
Maangta hoon main aur kuch bhi Kahan
Tu mujhe jo mile dard mere hansenge 
Kaash mujhko tu bhi yun hi chaahta 

Haar jaaun kahin toh junoon tu bane
Zindagi bhar ka mere sukoon tu bane 

Ab meri shaamein mere savere
Honge na tere bagair koi 
Dil mein hamesha tum hi rahoge 
Na aayega aur koi 
Hum bas tere hain 
Jab tak jiyenge tere hi rahenge 
Hum ye kah rahe hain 
Hum toh tere hain tere hi rahenge

#HarshvardhanRane #SonamBajwa #DeewaniyatKiDiwali #Diwali2025.

snippet.title: Love You Papa | Projapati 2 | Mithun C | Dev | Ishan | Jeet Gannguli | Avijit Senn | ‚Ä™Bengal Talkies
snippet.description:
Presenting the official video of ‚ÄúLove You Papa‚Äù from the much-awaited film Projapati 2‚Äîa heartfelt tribute to the unspoken bond between a father and child. The song beautifully captures the warmth and love that shape a family‚Äôs journey. With its touching lyrics and soulful melody, ‚ÄúLove You Papa‚Äù feels like a gentle reminder of the moments we often take for granted. The visuals add an emotional depth, portraying everyday memories that feel real, relatable, and deeply nostalgic.
 
Whether you‚Äôre watching with family or listening alone, this song leaves a soft ache in the heart and a smile on the face. It‚Äôs the kind of track that lingers long after it ends‚Äîperfect for anyone who cherishes the timeless connection between a father and child.

snippet.description:

snippet.title: Bulbul | Muhfaad | Kartavya | 2025
snippet.description:
Music/Mix/Master - Kartavya
Lyrics - Muhfaad 

Bandar chadha pahaad pe karke 
chutadh chaude
chup kyu hai baitha bol sorry behn ke!!

naach meri bulbul milega tujhe paisa
mita du teri chull mile jaise ko taisa
aaye na samajh tujhe izzat ka lehza
bewaqoof nahi dekha tere jaisa.

aadhe ganje 
adhe rapper
adhi shakti 
adhi mehnat
kaise sun lu 
kyu lu seh kar
kaun behtar
you know better

muhfaad kare muh pe blabber
rate hue sabke pattern
tu hi monseure tu hi madam
wig laga ke lagte karen

chidhta hai to chidhta reh
mai to karu daya na
kauwa kha ke goo
kis muh se bane sayana?

bat suno bhaijaan
muh pe maru paaydaan
faltu jo khaye kaan
to sareaam fir trahimam

leta kaun tujhe serious
get ready for veer ras
banda nahi tu gimmick 
Mr. idiot on periods.
chahye nahi opinion
mai 16 se nahi lenient
karu break character tera 
lo so that you can be real

ye koi beef wala nyauta nahi
tujhe bhaunkne se roka nahi
yad dilau doodh chhati ka par
hazam tujhe hoga nahi
soongh bagle aur kachhiyan
tu aur kisi jogga nahi
likhne se chutkule 
muqabla hoga nahi.

tere jaisi thuki mile
road pe baleno
mai bas dikhta hu akela
aake maarte hai teeno
mere jaise likhna hai to 
lagenge maheeno 
tujhe koi bhi na dhoondhe
agar hota bhi tu nemo

firse chadha bali 
haththe UP wale ke
tere area ke laundo
ko duty baatenge
ise sapno ki duniya se kheech ke laao
sare aate jate bulbul ko chooti katenge

apas ke mazak mat la screen pe
yahan baksha nahi kisi ko maine scene me
ye goat kya hai puchhte hai memne
bhosdi ke sote ke de dunga neend me.
